#: ../../user_guide.rst:2
msgid "AI Social Scientist 使用指南"
msgstr "AI Social Scientist User Guide"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:4
msgid ""
"**AI Social Scientist** 是 AgentSociety 2 的交互式研究助手，以 VSCode "
"扩展的形式提供可视化配置、后端管理和研究编排能力。它支持两种使用方式："
msgstr ""
"**AI Social Scientist** is the interactive research assistant for "
"AgentSociety 2, provided as a VSCode extension that offers visual "
"configuration, backend management, and research orchestration capabilities. "
"It supports two usage modes:"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:6
msgid "**在线工作空间**：通过网页平台直接使用，无需本地安装，适合快速上手。"
msgstr ""
"**Online Workspace**: Use directly through the web platform, no local "
"installation required, ideal for quick onboarding."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:7
msgid "**本地开发**：在本地安装扩展和依赖，适合需要自定义环境的高级用户。"
msgstr ""
"**Local Development**: Install the extension and dependencies locally, "
"suitable for advanced users who need a customized environment."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:12
msgid "在线工作空间"
msgstr "Online Workspace"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:14
msgid ""
"我们推荐使用在线平台进行实验，平台已预装 agentsociety2 库、AI Social Scientist 插件和 Claude Code "
"CLI。"
msgstr ""
"We recommend using the online platform for experiments. The platform comes "
"pre-installed with the agentsociety2 library, the AI Social Scientist "
"extension, and the Claude Code CLI."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:16
msgid "平台地址：https://agentsociety2.fiblab.net/"
msgstr "Platform URL: https://agentsociety2.fiblab.net/"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:19
msgid "注册与登录"
msgstr "Registration and Login"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:21
msgid "打开平台主页，点击\"登录\"。"
msgstr "Open the platform homepage and click \"Login\"."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:23
msgid "平台登录页面"
msgstr "Platform login page"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:27
msgid "如果没有账号，点击\"注册\"完成注册流程。已有 FIBLAB 账号的用户可直接登录。"
msgstr ""
"If you don't have an account, click \"Register\" to complete the "
"registration process. Users with an existing FIBLAB account can log in "
"directly."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:29
msgid "注册页面"
msgstr "Registration page"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:35
msgid "登录成功后，您可能需要联系平台管理员审批账号权限，审批通过后刷新页面即可。"
msgstr ""
"After logging in, you may need to contact the platform administrator to "
"approve your account permissions. Once approved, refresh the page."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:38 ../../user_guide.rst:42
msgid "创建工作空间"
msgstr "Create a Workspace"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:40
msgid "进入工作区管理页面，点击\"创建工作空间\"，输入名称后确认。"
msgstr ""
"Go to the workspace management page, click \"Create Workspace\", enter a "
"name and confirm."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:46
msgid "等待工作空间状态从\"创建中\"变为\"运行中\"。"
msgstr "Wait for the workspace status to change from \"Creating\" to \"Running\"."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:48
msgid "工作空间运行中"
msgstr "Workspace running"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:52
msgid "点击工作空间可查看 **Coder 账号密码**、 **免费 LLM API 端点**和 **API Key** 等信息，请妥善保存。"
msgstr ""
"Click on the workspace to view **Coder credentials**, **free LLM API "
"endpoint**, and **API Key** information. Please save these securely."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:54
msgid "工作空间账号与 API 信息"
msgstr "Workspace credentials and API information"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:58
msgid "复制页面上方的 Coder 账号信息，点击\"打开\"进入开发环境。"
msgstr ""
"Copy the Coder credentials shown at the top of the page, then click "
"\"Open\" to enter the development environment."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:60
msgid "Coder 登录"
msgstr "Coder login"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:64
msgid "在 Coder 页面中选择 **code-server** （推荐）或 **VS Code Desktop** 打开开发环境。"
msgstr ""
"On the Coder page, select **code-server** (recommended) or **VS Code "
"Desktop** to open the development environment."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:66
msgid "选择 code-server 或 VSCode Desktop"
msgstr "Select code-server or VSCode Desktop"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:70
msgid "code-server 界面"
msgstr "code-server interface"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:77
msgid "本地环境安装"
msgstr "Local Installation"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:80
msgid "前置条件"
msgstr "Prerequisites"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:82
msgid "**操作系统**：macOS 或 Linux（Windows 用户建议使用 WSL）"
msgstr "**Operating System**: macOS or Linux (Windows users should use WSL)"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:83
msgid "**Python**：3.11 或更高版本，推荐使用 `uv <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/>`_ 管理"
msgstr ""
"**Python**: 3.11 or higher. We recommend using `uv <https://docs.astral.sh/uv/>`_ "
"for management"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:91
msgid "安装 agentsociety2"
msgstr "Install agentsociety2"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:104
msgid "请确保安装的是最新版本。查看当前最新版本：https://pypi.org/project/agentsociety2/"
msgstr ""
"Make sure you are installing the latest version. Check the current latest "
"version at: https://pypi.org/project/agentsociety2/"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:107
msgid "安装 AI Social Scientist 插件"
msgstr "Install the AI Social Scientist Extension"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:109
msgid ""
"从 `Release <https://github.com/tsinghua-fib-lab/AgentSociety/releases>`_ "
"下载最新版本的 VSIX 文件。"
msgstr ""
"Download the latest VSIX file from the `Release page <https://github.com/tsinghua-fib-lab/AgentSociety/releases>`_."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:110
msgid ""
"在 VSCode 中按 ``Cmd/Ctrl + Shift + P``，输入 ``Extensions: Install from "
"VSIX...``。"
msgstr ""
"In VSCode, press ``Cmd/Ctrl + Shift + P``, type ``Extensions: Install from "
"VSIX...``."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:111
msgid "选择下载的 VSIX 文件完成安装。"
msgstr "Select the downloaded VSIX file to complete the installation."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:114
msgid "配置 Coding Agent"
msgstr "Configure the Coding Agent"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:116
msgid ""
"插件初始化工作区时会自动同步 AI Social Scientist 的技能到 ``.claude/skills/`` "
"目录下。您也可以点击侧边栏的\"同步 AI 助手资源\"手动同步。"
msgstr ""
"When the extension initializes a workspace, it automatically syncs AI "
"Social Scientist skills to the ``.claude/skills/`` directory. You can also "
"click \"Sync AI Assistant Resources\" in the sidebar to sync manually."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:118
msgid "同步 AI 助手资源"
msgstr "Sync AI assistant resources"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:122
msgid "Claude Code（推荐）："
msgstr "Claude Code (recommended):"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:128
msgid "配置第三方中转服务时，创建 ``~/.claude/settings.json``："
msgstr ""
"When configuring a third-party proxy service, create "
"``~/.claude/settings.json``:"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:140
msgid "也可以安装 Claude Code 的 VSCode 插件，点击扩展侧边栏的\"AI 对话\"后会直接弹出 Claude Code 对话页面："
msgstr ""
"You can also install the Claude Code VSCode extension. Clicking \"AI Chat\" "
"in the extension sidebar will open the Claude Code chat panel directly:"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:142
msgid "Claude Code VSCode 集成"
msgstr "Claude Code VSCode integration"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:148
msgid ""
"同步到 ``.claude/skills/`` 的技能可被 Claude Code 和 Cursor 自动识别。插件也会自动为 CodeX "
"创建符号链接（``.codex``），无需手动操作。"
msgstr ""
"Skills synced to ``.claude/skills/`` are automatically recognized by Claude "
"Code and Cursor. The extension also creates a symbolic link for CodeX "
"(``.codex``) automatically — no manual action needed."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:153
msgid "环境配置"
msgstr "Environment Configuration"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:156
msgid "新建工作区"
msgstr "Create a New Workspace"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:158
msgid "在线工作空间中，在左侧文件树新建一个文件夹作为工作区（如 ``demo``），然后通过 ``File → Open Folder`` 打开。"
msgstr ""
"In the online workspace, create a new folder in the left file tree as your "
"workspace (e.g., ``demo``), then open it via ``File → Open Folder``."

