msgid "启动后端"
msgstr "Start the Backend"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:240
msgid "配置完成后点击\"保存并启动后端\"，系统会自动保存配置并启动后端服务。右下角状态栏显示后端运行状态（含端口号）表示启动成功。"
msgstr ""
"After configuration, click \"Save & Start Backend\". The system will "
"automatically save the configuration and start the backend service. The "
"status bar in the bottom-right corner showing the backend running status "
"(with port number) indicates a successful start."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:242
msgid "配置验证成功"
msgstr "Configuration validation successful"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:246
msgid "后端运行状态"
msgstr "Backend running status"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:253
msgid "开始研究"
msgstr "Start Research"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:256 ../../user_guide.rst:260
msgid "初始化工作区"
msgstr "Initialize Workspace"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:258
msgid ""
"后端启动成功后，在插件页面点击\"初始化工作区\"，输入研究话题（如 \"polarization\"）并回车。系统会自动创建 "
"``TOPIC.md`` 和相关目录结构。"
msgstr ""
"After the backend starts successfully, click \"Initialize Workspace\" in "
"the extension panel, enter a research topic (e.g., \"polarization\") and "
"press Enter. The system will automatically create ``TOPIC.md`` and the "
"relevant directory structure."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:264
msgid "``TOPIC.md`` 是贯穿整个研究流程的核心文档，您可以随时手动编辑来补充研究描述、背景信息和研究方向。"
msgstr ""
"``TOPIC.md`` is the central document throughout the research process. You "
"can edit it at any time to add research descriptions, background "
"information, and research directions."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:267
msgid "与 Claude Code 协作"
msgstr "Collaborate with Claude Code"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:269
