msgstr ""
"We recommend following the sequence below, but each stage can be revisited "
"or skipped at any time:"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:293
msgid "各阶段说明见 :doc:`skills`。"
msgstr "For details on each stage, see :doc:`skills`."

