#: ../../user_guide.rst:332
msgid "常见问题"
msgstr "FAQ"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:335
msgid "code-server 显示 unhealthy"
msgstr "code-server shows unhealthy"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:337
msgid "初次创建工作空间时，后端服务可能正在启动中。稍等片刻后刷新页面，等待状态变为绿色的 \"Running\"。如果持续出现，可以尝试重启工作区。"
msgstr ""
"When creating a workspace for the first time, the backend service may still "
"be starting. Wait a moment and refresh the page until the status changes to "
"a green \"Running\". If the issue persists, try restarting the workspace."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:340
msgid "打开 code-server 后显示 502 错误"
msgstr "502 error when opening code-server"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:342
msgid "后端服务未正确启动，请耐心等待后刷新页面。如果问题持续存在，请查看后端日志或联系平台管理员。"
msgstr ""
"The backend service has not started correctly. Please wait and refresh the "
"page. If the problem persists, check the backend logs or contact the "
"platform administrator."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:345
msgid "本地 Python 环境路径问题"
msgstr "Local Python environment path issues"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:347
msgid "在线平台预装了 Python 环境，本地使用时（尤其是通过 uv 创建的虚拟环境），需要在高级配置中指定正确的 Python 路径："
msgstr ""
"The online platform has Python pre-installed. For local usage (especially "
"with virtual environments created via uv), you need to specify the correct "
"Python path in the advanced configuration:"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:354
msgid "将输出的路径填入配置向导\"后端服务\"步骤的 Python 路径字段。"
msgstr ""
"Enter the output path in the Python path field of the \"Backend Service\" "
"step in the configuration wizard."

#: ../../user_guide.rst:357
msgid "实验运行失败"
msgstr "Experiment execution failed"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:359
msgid "常见原因："
msgstr "Common causes:"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:361
msgid "**LLM API 连接失败**：检查 ``.env`` 中的 API 配置是否正确"
msgstr "**LLM API connection failure**: Check the API configuration in ``.env``"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:362
msgid "**模块实例化失败**：检查 ``init_config.json`` 中的参数是否与模块要求一致"
msgstr "**Module instantiation failure**: Check that the parameters in ``init_config.json`` match the module requirements"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:363
msgid "**内存不足**：减少智能体数量或仿真步数"
msgstr "**Insufficient memory**: Reduce the number of agents or simulation steps"

#: ../../user_guide.rst:365
msgid "更多 CLI 使用方法见 :doc:`cli`，研究技能详见 :doc:`skills`。"
msgstr "For more CLI usage, see :doc:`cli`. For research skills, see :doc:`skills`."
